<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.11">
<l>aḵtē yuyyap pukumāṟeṉṟu kaṇṇaṉ kaḻalkaḷmēl</l>
<l>koypūm poḻilcūḻ kurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ kuṟṟēval</l>
<l>ceykōlat tāyirañ cīrttoṭaip pāṭa livaipattum</l>
<l>aḵkāmaṟ kaṟpava rāḻtuyar pōyuyyaṟ pālarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who learn without reduction</l>
<l>these ten songs linked with rhythm in the beautiful thousand made</l>
<l>as a service by Caṭakōpān of Kurukūr, surrounded by groves of plucked flowers,</l>
<l>on the ankletted [feet] of Kṛṣṇa thinking that is the way to go about in order to escape</l>
	<l>will have the fate of going [and] escaping sinking misery.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
